reviewText: Bret Harte's Gold Rush: Outcasts of Poker Flat, the Luck of Roaring Camp, Tennessee's Partner, & Other FavoritesBret Harte Stories of the Early West: The Luck of Roaring Camp and 16 Other Exciting Tales of Mining and Frontier Days From the CLASSICS ILLUSTRATED TV SERIES. Wonderful, light-hearted family fare about the opening of the West in the Gold Rush era with some nostalgic actors that aren't with us anymore. From the makers of GRIZZLY ADAMS. With Ken (Festus) Curtis and Dan Haggerty
